Help Google:
Webmaster tools (https://www.google.com/webmasters/tools/home?hl=fr) for Google (you need a Google account to access).
Help Center dedicated to webmasters: https://support.google.com/webmasters/?hl=fr#topic=3309469.

Help Bing:
Webmaster tools (http://www.bing.com/toolbox/webmaster) for Bing (you need a Microsoft account to access).